title: Microsoft Entra: Conditional Access VPN Certificate
agents: entra
catalog: cloud/Microsoft
license: GPLv2
distribution: Christopher Pommer
description:
 This check monitors the expiration time of certificates
 from the Entra Conditional Access VPN enterprise application
 (service principal) with the name "VPN Server".

 The levels {OK}, {WARN} and {CRIT} depends on the
 configured check levels for the certificate expiration time.

 You have to configure the special agent {Microsoft Entra}.

discovery:
 One service is created for the VPN Server enterprise application.
